original_title: Star Wars: The Clone Wars - The Nightsisters Trilogy
overview: A home video compilation film of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars episodes "Nightsisters," "Monster," and "Witches of the Mist," cut together. Originally shown at select screenings in 2010 (mainly at conventions), and it was published as an iTunes digital download on December 5, 2011.
title: Star Wars: The Clone Wars - The Nightsisters Trilogy
